"This week the Platform Cooperativism Consortium hosted its second Platform Co-op Community Hangout as part of our ongoing series of discussions with organizers, activists, scholars, entreprenuers and workers focused on building a new digital economy.

We were pleased to host Micky Metts, a member of Agaric, a worker-owned cooperative of web developers. Known as Free Scholar on Twitter, Micky is an activist hacker, industry organizer, public speaker, connector, and cooperative visionary."

